<paragraph id="6D0836D113175C49FF15FB07CEA3FB41" blockId="19.[174,1233,1178,1332]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">
Distribution. Widespread European species, has been reported also from the Oriental Region (
<bibRefCitation id="09264B2013175C49FE89FB27CF69FB60" author="Papp, L. &amp; Cerny, M." box="[383,636,1210,1237]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472" refId="ref19613" refString="Papp, L. &amp; Cerny, M. 2015. Agromyzidae (Diptera) of Hungary. Volume 1. Agromyzinae. Nagykovacsi, Pars Ltd., 1 - 416. DOI: http: // doi. org / 10.18655 / Agromyzidae. Vol. 1." type="book" year="2015">Papp &amp; Černý, 2015</bibRefCitation>
). 
<emphasis id="5FC3EAC313175C49FD64FB27CE36FB61" bold="true" box="[658,803,1210,1236]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">
In 
<collectingCountry id="15A0764113175C49FD4EFB27CE0BFB61" box="[696,798,1210,1236]" name="Ukraine" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
.
</emphasis>
<collectingRegion id="AF73F83313175C49FCDBFB27CE9AFB61" box="[813,911,1210,1236]" country="Ukraine" name="Kharkiv" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Kharkiv</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="AF73F83313175C49FC6BFB27CEE2FB61" box="[925,1015,1210,1236]" country="Ukraine" name="Poltava" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Poltava</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="AF73F83313175C49FBF2FB27C952FB61" box="[1028,1095,1210,1236]" country="Ukraine" name="Sumy" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Sumy</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion id="AF73F83313175C49FB7EFB27C9C4FB61" box="[1160,1233,1210,1236]" country="Ukraine" name="Volyn'" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Volyn</collectingRegion>
Regions (
<bibRefCitation id="09264B2013175C49FEEDFB47CCACFB41" author="Guglya, Yu." box="[283,441,1242,1268]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472" pagination="61 - 68" refId="ref19059" refString="Guglya, Yu. 2011. A study of the fauna of leaf-miner flies of the subfamily Agromyzinae (Diptera: Agromyzidae) of Ukraine. Report 1. 28 new species for the fauna of Ukraine. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette, 19 (2), 61 - 68 [In Russian]." type="journal article" year="2011">Guglya, 2011</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="09264B2013175C49FE32FB47CCEAFB40" author="Guglya, Yu." box="[452,511,1242,1269]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472" pagination="29 - 38" refId="ref19304" refString="Guglya, Yu. 2015. A study of the fauna of leaf-miner flies of the subfamily Agromyzinae (Diptera: Agromyzidae) of Ukraine. Report 3. Eleven new species for the fauna of Ukraine. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette, 23 (2), 29 - 38." type="journal article" year="2015">2015</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="09264B2013175C49FDFFFB47CF53FB40" author="Guglya, Yu." box="[521,582,1242,1269]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472" pagination="48 - 56" refId="ref19484" refString="Guglya, Yu. 2017. A study of the fauna of leaf-miner flies of the subfamily Agromyzinae (Diptera: Agromyzidae) of Ukraine. Report 5. Seven new species for the fauna of Ukraine. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette, 25 (1), 48 - 56." type="journal article" year="2017">2017</bibRefCitation>
); 
<collectingRegion id="AF73F83313175C49FDAFFB47CE1EFB41" box="[601,779,1242,1268]" country="Ukraine" name="Zakarpattya" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Transcarpathia</collectingRegion>
(
<emphasis id="5FC3EAC313175C49FCEAFB47CEB0FB41" bold="true" box="[796,933,1242,1268]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">first record</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6D0836D113175C49FF15FB67CF5EFA81" blockId="19.[174,1233,1178,1332]" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">
Bionomics. Widespread and common in 
<collectingCountry id="15A0764113175C49FCE4FB67CE60FAA1" box="[786,885,1274,1300]" name="Ukraine" pageId="19" pageNumber="472">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
. Adults were uncommonly collected from 1 May to 24 August.
</paragraph>
